'''Daedalic Entertainment GmbH''' is a German videogame publisher and developer and it is based in Hamburg.In 2022, it was acquired by [[Nacon]] company.<ref>{{webcite|articleurl=https://corporate.nacongaming.com/en/press/daedalic-acquisition-definitive/|articlename= Definitive acquisition of Daedalic Entertainment|dated=17-April-2022|website=Nacon Corporate|accessed=24-March-2023}}</ref> It is the publishing company of the videogame [[The Lord of the Rings: Gollum]].
